group.post_content: Enter the URL for your Private Portal page.

Fill out this form to create a new card or quick link.

field.name: Link Type
field.description: Select the option for what you would like this card to link to.

field.name: Internal Link
field.description: Choose the page of this portal you would like to link to.

field.name: External Link
field.description: Enter the full URL of the site you would like to link to.

field.name: File Upload
field.description: Upload the file you want this card to link to.

field.name: New Tab
field.description: Select if you want this link to open in a new browser tab.

field.name: Card Image
field.description: Upload the image you want to have appear on this card or quick link. For a card the image should be 130px by 85px, quick link images should be 48px by 48px

field.name: Disable
field.description: Select if you want this card to be disabled

field.name: Disabled Message
field.description: Enter the message you would like to see appear on the card when it is disabled

field.name: Resource Type
field.description: Choose what kind of resource this is or if you want it to be marked as coming soon.
Choose the operating system this browser is for
field.name: Operating System

field.description: Enter the versions of the operating system this browser is compatible with.
field.name: OS Version

field.description: upload the icon for this version of the secure browser
field.name: Browser Version Icon

field.description: enter the text to describe this version of the secure browsers and any information a user may need to install it.
field.name: Browser Information

field.description: Upload the secure browser file so users can download it.
